==French==

===Phrase===
'''[[brûler]] [[la]] [[chandelle]] [[par]] [[les]] [[deux]] [[bouts]]'''

# To live life too fast, doing everything in excess, including spending too much money, working too hard, going without sleep, and abusing all good things and pleasures (literally: to burn the candle at both ends).

